description: Some days are just strange. It doesn´t matter how many guys I approach: they all reject my offers... even guys with "average looks" are not interested. And today was such a day. I spent almost 2 hours there until I finally found "my guy". Blond, quite cute, funny and somehow with character. He even had a good salary so again I had to offer a lot to get what I want. And: he was shy. Finally he showed me at least his bare chest. I don´t even know why he was so shy. He had a good body. Tanned and trained. And after he made his first 1,000 crowns he wanted to run away. So I had to start again persuading him for giving me a hand-job. Can you imagine how difficult it was to get a blow-job?
title: Czech Hunter 108
